                                                Telecommunication and Information Technology Framework as a means to
                                                achieve its desired goals in the Libyan ICT sector
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </section>
                        <div class="oe_structure"/>
